# Track only the original Cairo source TTFs (license: SIL OFL).
# Everything else in this directory is auto-generated by DomPDF on
# first PDF render — `.ufm`, `.ufm.json`, hash-suffixed `.ttf`
# subset caches, and `installed-fonts.json` — and is regenerable
# from the source files. Do NOT track those.

# Default deny.
*

# Allow this gitignore.
!.gitignore

# Allow source fonts (committed; license: SIL OFL).
# Arabic is handled by mPDF's bundled DejaVu Sans, so no Arabic
# TTF lives here (Phase 6.5 — earlier Cairo "arabic" subset had
# missing glyphs; tested replacements like Amiri / Noto Naskh
# Arabic, but mPDF 8.3 cannot parse their advanced GPOS tables).
!Cairo-Latin-Regular.ttf
!Cairo-Latin-Bold.ttf
